{"id": "1488892461567967383", "channel_id": "1488892461567967383", "type": 0, "author_id": "1280181546527096993", "author_name": "fjantsa", "author_bot": false, "content": "The numbers seems wrong? picking the effect says 10/11, the buff says 7/7, actual gain is +7 str.\n\nScreenshots from D-tide 3 (tulu) alert 3, \nMiryam lvl 64, E3+1\nCon/atk/def\n99/156/85\nRouse lvl 6\nSoulforge 5/10\n\nI am assuming the actual issue is due to Goliaths Lemurian passive;\n\"When there are 1/2/3 other \"Lemurian\" Awakeners in the team, all Awakeners' STR generation is increased by 6%/15%/30%\"\nIt seems this does not properly apply to the Revelate Devotion buff.\nI have not tested whether the other lemurian passives actually function as they should (Miryams should give tentacle dmg gain, etc)\n\nI tested with Miryam and 3 chaos units, and the card displayed 7STR/8Tent damage, and correctly applied +7 str.\n\nIt also seems the buff description is \"lying\" a little, it implies it gives the same str and tentacle DMG, but since effects can increase str gain and tentacle dmg separately, its not necessarily the same number for both effects.", "timestamp": "2026-04-01T13:27:05.122000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-01T13:45:02.065000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1488892461978746961", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/webp", "size": 236630, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1488892461567967383/1488892461978746961/image.png?ex=69ce6ea9&is=69cd1d29&hm=93566d812978120ad43203666248ae690468579eee49226cd96ca3057127bab5&"}, {"id": "1488892462352175274", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 713898, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1488892461567967383/1488892462352175274/image.png?ex=69ce6ea9&is=69cd1d29&hm=b58014f22ce939cc096b90840245b1fc63329a38670a94468ee63793c673addd&"}, {"id": "1488892462805028996", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 544873, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1488892461567967383/1488892462805028996/image.png?ex=69ce6ea9&is=69cd1d29&hm=67a1a47634282277a4742bf0a81e4d28e628f375d4f86fd75b7912e6fd0cb9fc&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1488892461567967383", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Miryam Revelate Devotion str/tentacle dmg gain", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168893200044183"]}
